This circular follows all previous dengue circulars and reviews all
epidemiological information available at the present time.
Countries and territories appear in the table below in chronological order,
according to the date the current Dengue-2 (DEN-2) virus epidemic began.
1. Summary of DEN-2 virus situation as reported by Pacific Island countries
and territories:
